{"tid":1612623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再恐慌性大叫 \"有狗\"  / 掉頭跑","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T02:13:33.000Z","uid":24845,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2d4a74faed28fcfb58a71f5b8227688181ff13a1","tid":1612623,"uid":24845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:02:23.000Z","msg":"要驚要縮無問題<br />\n冷靜多一兩分, 講低咩事, 咩位置左右幾多隻, <br />\n真係要退既慢慢退<br />\n恐懼會傳染,唔好搞到人心惶惶, 唔該"},{"pid":"0476c046e710848e5218aa379e137b564a79d9f5","tid":1612623,"uid":287792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"叫打狗"},{"pid":"2edf95e88b00750d725159b8d77ec4d7785eec24","tid":1612623,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗叫 我地咁多人 點解要走"},{"pid":"7378f6346351e1a70818b81feaad26bf7de25f75","tid":1612623,"uid":238301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"同埋唔好再唱啊死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd651f2e6cbe80e2b9b55cf2e392ad0f6b353564","tid":1612623,"uid":299276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:10:51.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"d7b804f26a97e31ec40134266eabc878ccbf0062","tid":1612623,"uid":292777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"真，有時d恐懼心理仲恐怖過事物本身。<br />\n<br />\n都未肯定，就一叫有狗就慌忙咁走，然後傳染恐懼心理，一傳10，10傳百。繼續係咁，就算人數係狗100倍都冇用，狗只會恥笑我地烏合之眾。<br />\n<br />\n無錯，和理非係充下人數，但都應該做個冷靜少少既和理非，比班前線見到咁樣，仲有咩士氣可言。當然，我唔係話有成堆full gear 狗都唔走，大前提真係要先確定(呢個就哨兵做多步，要講清楚方向，數量，種類)，然後先退，退既時候最好唔好背對班狗，如果我地人多，正面對住再向後退，反而咁樣仲安全。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 充人數和理非，但唔想雷前線。琴日有去沙田睇住咁樣大家自己嚇自己。"},{"pid":"53a0ba186c647c805de0ea2ff36072e162b8ce51","tid":1612623,"uid":24845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:53:17.000Z","msg":"有狗唔係要退<br />\n係要進<br />\n幾千人對幾十個<br />\n怕撚過鬼咁<br />\n傻豬黎既"},{"pid":"913a14aefb3d617b0c27c63bc8137428c131919f","tid":1612623,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"掉頭跑好容易會搞到其他自己友落單被捕，d狗好鐘意突然間跑上前。"},{"pid":"1b32aa8bec2f39dc5962293dff6d2b89afd9fa05","tid":1612623,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7378f6346351e1a70818b81feaad26bf7de25f75","tid":1612623,"uid":238301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"同埋唔好再唱啊死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"？？"},{"pid":"5acbe098632828ac10241049f1aac1c50069c5f7","tid":1612623,"uid":24845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b32aa8bec2f39dc5962293dff6d2b89afd9fa05","tid":1612623,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7378f6346351e1a70818b81feaad26bf7de25f75","tid":1612623,"uid":238301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"同埋唔好再唱啊死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"果下 &quot;啊&quot; 既尖叫聲好多人會以為有事發生。"},{"pid":"0eb5ccd69b9bdc7a36fc47c5ea2ba5c9dfc97098","tid":1612623,"uid":24845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:06:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e3a65a32bd67fb65e6e88e4539d71439415ba7c8","tid":1612623,"uid":48168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2edf95e88b00750d725159b8d77ec4d7785eec24","tid":1612623,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗叫 我地咁多人 點解要走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:13:33.000Z","msg":"打又唔夠打，又話打游擊點解要同狗正面對打？除咗保護和理非撤退外，諗唔到仲有咩理由。"}]}